      "date": "2012-08-03 22:48:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d3298f90-ddb8-11e1-a041-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
